{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setemail:completion:"]}],"metadata":{"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"setEmail:completion:"}],"externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)setEmail:completion:","roleHeading":"Type Method","symbolKind":"method","role":"symbol","title":"setEmail:completion:","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setEmail:completion:"}],"modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}]},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setEmail:","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"NSString","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"email"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"completion:"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":" (^"},{"text":")(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSError","text":"NSError","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":" * "},{"text":"error","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":")) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"completion"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"parameters":[{"name":"email","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The user’s email address. Must be a valid email format."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Block called when the operation completes."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Receives nil on success, or an NSError on failure."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"completion"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Same as "},{"code":"setEmail:","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" but provides callback when the server registration completes.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Use this when you need to:"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Verify email was registered before showing confirmation UI","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Chain operations that depend on email registration","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Implement error handling and retry logic"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"text":"Example","anchor":"Example","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Register email during account setup with verification:","type":"text"}]},{"code":["class AccountSetupController {","","    func submitEmail(_ email: String) {","        guard isValidEmail(email) else {","            showError(\"Please enter a valid email address\")","            return","        }","","        showLoadingState()","","        Pushwoosh.configure.setEmail(email) { [weak self] error in","            DispatchQueue.main.async {","                self?.hideLoadingState()","","                if let error = error {","                    Logger.error(\"Email registration failed: \\(error.localizedDescription)\")","                    self?.showRetryOption(for: email)","                    return","                }","","                \/\/ Email registered successfully - update tags","                let domain = email.components(separatedBy: \"@\").last ?? \"\"","                Pushwoosh.configure.setTags([","                    \"has_email\": true,","                    \"email_domain\": domain,","                    \"email_type\": self?.classifyEmailDomain(domain) ?? \"personal\"","                ])","","                self?.proceedToNextStep()","            }","        }","    }","","    private func classifyEmailDomain(_ domain: String) -> String {","        let businessDomains = [\"company.com\", \"enterprise.org\"]","        let educationDomains = [\"edu\", \"ac.uk\", \"edu.au\"]","","        if businessDomains.contains(domain) { return \"business\" }","        if educationDomains.contains(where: { domain.hasSuffix($0) }) { return \"education\" }","        return \"personal\"","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"}]}],"sections":[],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setEmail:completion:"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Associates an email address with the current device with completion confirmation."}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/setEmail:completion:":{"type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setEmail:completion:","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Associates an email address with the current device with completion confirmation."}],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setemail:completion:","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setEmail:completion:","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","title":"setEmail:completion:","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setEmail:completion:"}]},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"abstract":[],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"PWConfiguration"}],"title":"PWConfiguration","type":"topic","role":"symbol"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","kind":"symbol","role":"collection","title":"PushwooshCore","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}]}}}